In re ZEREGA’S WILL. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. February 16, 1894.) Proceeding to revoke probate of the will of Augustus Zerega, deceased.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. X, and O’BRIEN and FOLLETT, JX

No opinion. Order affirmed, without costs. See 20 N. Y. Supp. 417.
